[470] (w=84) " \u001b[38;2;240;198;116m\u001b[1m### \u001b[22m\u001b[39m\u001b[38;2;240;198;116m\u001b[1mAdded\u001b[22m\u001b[39m                                                                          "
[471] (w=84) "                                                                                    "
[472] (w=84) " \u001b[38;2;138;190;183m- \u001b[39mAdded extension support for customizing the interactive streaming working        "
[473] (w=84) " indicator via \u001b[38;2;138;190;183mctx.ui.setWorkingIndicator()\u001b[39m, including custom animated frames,      "
