[511] (w=84) " the active coding-agent session cwd instead of the launcher cwd (\u001b]8;;https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono/issues/3452\u001b\\\u001b[38;2;129;162;190m\u001b[4m#3452\u001b[24m\u001b[39m\u001b]8;;\u001b\\)            "
[512] (w=84) " \u001b[38;2;138;190;183m- \u001b[39mFixed \u001b[38;2;138;190;183mctx.ui.setWorkingIndicator()\u001b[39m custom frames to render verbatim instead of   "
[513] (w=84) " forcing the theme accent color, so extensions now own working-indicator coloring   "
[514] (w=84) " when they customize it (\u001b]8;;https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono/issues/3467\u001b\\\u001b[38;2;129;162;190m\u001b[4m#3467\u001b[24m\u001b[39m\u001b]8;;\u001b\\)                                                     "
[515] (w=84) " \u001b[38;2;138;190;183m- \u001b[39mFixed \u001b[38;2;138;190;183mpi update\u001b[39m reinstalling npm packages that are already at the latest         "
