[528] (w=84) " \u001b[38;2;138;190;183mcacheRetention\u001b[39m to prompt caching fields, sending \u001b[38;2;138;190;183mprompt_cache_key\u001b[39m when caching is  "
[529] (w=84) " enabled and \u001b[38;2;138;190;183mprompt_cache_retention: \"24h\"\u001b[39m for direct \u001b[38;2;138;190;183mapi.openai.com\u001b[39m requests with  "
