[535] (w=84) " \u001b[38;2;138;190;183m- \u001b[39mFixed threaded \u001b[38;2;138;190;183m/resume\u001b[39m session relationships and current-session detection to    "
[536] (w=84) " canonicalize symlinked session paths during selector comparisons, so shared        "
