[549] (w=84) " \u001b[38;2;138;190;183mmodifyOtherKeys\u001b[39m input and normalizing shifted letter matching, so \u001b[38;2;138;190;183mShift+letter\u001b[39m no  "
[550] (w=84) " longer disappears in \u001b[38;2;138;190;183mpi\u001b[39m (\u001b]8;;https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono/issues/3436\u001b\\\u001b[38;2;129;162;190m\u001b[4m#3436\u001b[24m\u001b[39m\u001b]8;;\u001b\\)                                                    "
[551] (w=84) " \u001b[38;2;138;190;183m- \u001b[39mFixed \u001b[38;2;138;190;183m/compact\u001b[39m to reuse the session thinking level for compaction summaries      "
[552] (w=84) " instead of forcing \u001b[38;2;138;190;183mhigh\u001b[39m, avoiding invalid reasoning-effort errors on               "
