[626] (w=84) " forwarding \u001b[38;2;138;190;183mdetails\u001b[39m and \u001b[38;2;138;190;183misError\u001b[39m overrides through \u001b[38;2;138;190;183mAgentSession\u001b[39m instead of dropping  "
